snippet: Rex Ryan praised Jets practices this week even as his job, along with that of General Manager Mike Tannenbaum and the backup quarterback Tim Tebow, could be in jeopardy.
abstract: New York Jets coach Rex Ryan praises his team for their efforts during practice even as his job, along with that of general manager Mike Tannenbaum and backup quarterback Tim Tebow, could be in jeopardy.
lead_paragraph: Rex Ryan praised Jets practices this week even as his job, along with that of General Manager Mike Tannenbaum and the backup quarterback Tim Tebow, could be in jeopardy.

headline.seo: Jets, After Days of Negative Talk, Try to Shift Focus to the Positive
headline.main: Jets Ready to Play Ball; Apparently, It Will Still Be Football
